<html t:type="layoutImageau" title="Editing File  "
	xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd" xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">



	<h1>CheckboxGroup demo</h1>

	A simple example to illustrate how to use component ControlCB and
	mixin
	ControlledCheckbox to get a check box group.
	The source code of this
	demo
	is
	<br />
	<form t:type="form" t:id="myForm">

		<br />
		<table>

			<tr t:type="loop" source="smds" value="smd">
				<td>
					<t:checkbox value="selected" />
					${smd}
				</td>
			</tr>

		</table>



		<input type="submit" value="Submit" />
	</form>





</html>
 
